      <p>Real estate is typically the largest single cost category. Dispensary-appropriate locations in Maine vary enormously by market. A converted retail space in rural Maine might cost $8,000-$15,000 to lease and build out, while a Portland-adjacent location with existing cannabis infrastructure might command $30,000-$50,000 in leasehold improvements alone.</p>

